<body>
 <h1>Protein Shake Recipe</h1>   
<p>
Here is the recipe for a protein shake!
</p>

<li>
<ul>1 scoop chocolate protein powder</ul>
<ul>1 scoop peanut butter powder</ul>
<ul>1 banana</ul>
<ul>1 scoop collagen</ul>
<ul>1 scoop creatine</ul>
<ul>2 cups almond or coconut milk</ul>
</li>


</body>
</html>